      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Benchmark problems from ASME V&V 10 and vendor-supplied verification suite demonstrate correct implementation of linear elastic solid elements.",
      "rationale": "Patch test and Cook's membrane benchmark cases reproduced analytical solutions to within 0.1%. Vendor verification manual results replicated. Gradation 2 achieved."
